//
// § T11-W17-F · canonical-CSSL-source · ‼ FOUNDATIONAL
//
// § APOCKY-CANONICAL · NON-NEGOTIABLE
//   1. PROPRIETARY local intelligence — NO Anthropic-API · NO OpenAI-API ·
//      NO external-LLM · NO phrase-pool tables · NO scripted-dialogue lookup.
//   2. PROCEDURAL-EVERYTHING — substrate primitives compose meaning at runtime.
//      ω-field stores semantic state · KAN-splines learn local-bias ·
//      HDC binds context⊗query → response · causal-seed reasons-about-effects ·
//      Σ-mask gates every emission.
//   3. LOCAL-ONLY data flow. Nothing leaves the device by default. Federated-
//      mycelium share is opt-in per-feedback_sigma_chain_unified_substrate.
//   4. DETERMINISTIC. Same (Context · Query · seed) → same Response, bit-for-bit,
//      across hosts + sessions. No thread-local entropy. No system-clock entropy.
//
// § REFERENCE
