// § PRIME-DIRECTIVE
//   The substrate_intelligence engine is the heart of LoA's proprietary AI.
//   It refuses-to-call any-external-LLM service. It refuses-to-emit on-Σ-mask-
//   denial. It refuses-to-train on-data without-attestation. It refuses-to-leak
//   per-player KAN-bias across-sigma-mask-boundaries. The 4 specialist roles
//   (DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder) all dispatch through this single canonical
//   surface. Every utterance, every decision, every composed-content carries
//   the attestation : there was no hurt nor harm in the making of this, to
//   anyone, anything, or anybody.
//
// § CSSLC-REQUIRES (capability-list current as-of 2026-05-01)
//   ✓ extern "C" fn  decls (csslc-W11+ · landed)
